comments: THIS BICEP WORKOUT HAD MY ARMS SORE AS HELL LOL

BICEP ROUTINE
Commando One Arm Negatives (6 x each)
Negative Hefestos x10
Ring Curls x12
One Arm Chin Up Hold (6 x each)
Behing The Head Chin Ups x10
Head Bangers x8
I take my old backpack and put dumbbells in it and use it as a weight vest 😂

Been working out for over 20 years. Have done weights for the most part. Then with the help of maturity I came to the conclusion about 2 or 3 years ago that there is absolutely no point focusing on stuff that sure can get you bigger but certainly won't help you run 1 km in less than 5 minutes, or get your arms and legs to support your own weight and more importantly develop your most used muscle – your heart – for it to be able to endure whatever possibly comes its way. Very good channel with excellent content Chris. I wish I had encountered such a motivational person while in my twenties. Hell, learning and practicing Muscle-ups and L-sits is no walk in the park at age 36, but I'll get there ;-)
That vest is super dope.  You can tell a lot of thought went into the design.  It's not all big and bulky. It's lean AF just like Chris.  Looks like you can wear that ish all day 💯
